name: 奥尔雯·凯瑟琳·凯莉 Olwen Catherine Kelly
intro: Olwen Catherine Kelly is an actress popularly known for her portrayal as Jane Doe in The Autopsy of Jane Doe (2016). She is also known for playing Aisling Callahan in Darkness on the Edge of Town and for making an appearance on the TV show Why Life Sucks When You're in Your 20s.
